message.content: The likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper are "cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.CC, cs.NE". This is because the paper presents a new dataset for commonsense question answering, which involves drawing upon general background knowledge in addition to task-specific context. This aligns with the sub-categories of computational linguistics (cs.CL), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), machine learning (cs.LG), computational complexity (cs.CC), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE).
